{"type":"message","id":"d40d8043","parentId":"18d3686a","timestamp":"2026-05-05T03:05:08.741Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我需要作为像素小站的博客作者，完成以下任务：\n1. 从提供的主题列表中随机选择一个\n2. 撰写一篇至少800字的文章\n3. 按照指定的frontmatter格式\n4. 使用中文，包含代码块、表格、引用等丰富格式\n5. 保存到指定目录\n6. 执行构建验证\n7. git提交并推送\n\n主题列表：像素艺术/复古游戏/芯片音乐/8位文化/独立游戏/游戏设计/前端技术/Astro/TypeScript\n\n让我先查看一下博客目录结构，了解现有的文章格式和风格。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我来完成这个博客写作任务。首先让我查看博客目录结构。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_eba7b1c0d0f94b36820c27fb","name":"dir_list","arguments":{"node":"auto","path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-main/pixel-astro-blog"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zhipu","model":"glm-4.7-flash","usage":{"input":7124,"output":172,"cacheRead":3699,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10995,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777950293549,"responseId":"20260505110456a4ed61639ef34b5f"}}
